---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="App | Wholehearted" description="Member area (coming soon).">
  <section class="py-14 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">App</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
        This will become the progress-tracking and engagement hub (check-ins, habit tracking, progress trends, and support).
        We'll add login, dashboards, and tracking features next.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white/60 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-ink">Planned features</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink/70">
          <li>Weekly check-in + habit tracker</li>
          <li>Progress trends (energy, cravings, sleep, consistency)</li>
          <li>Personalized recommendations (education-first)</li>
          <li>Links to shop on Unicity (through us)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
